702152f-a.title: Bronx: White Plains Road - 213th Street (East)
702152f-a.text:
White Plains Road, west side, between Bast 213th and East 216th
Streets (at the head of East 215th Street), showing St. Mary's Roman
Catholic Church.
November 11, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
